4. What are the key challenges faced by the 40-inch TV market? Price sensitivity, intense competition, and supply chain disruptions pose challenges to growth in the market.

5. Why are consumers opting for 40-inch TVs? Consumers prefer 40-inch TVs for their ideal balance of affordability, screen size, and picture quality for smaller living spaces.

