9. How do economic factors impact the 40-inch TV market? Economic conditions, including disposable income and consumer confidence, affect purchasing decisions and the demand for affordable TVs.

10. Will the 40-inch TV segment face stiff competition from larger screen sizes? Yes, larger screen sizes like 50-inch and 55-inch models may pose competition, but the 40-inch category remains popular due to its affordability and suitability for smaller spaces.

